00:03:26.865 --> 00:03:30.887
but there are friendly men out there
who have spare seeds.

00:03:31.386 --> 00:03:33.136
They bring them to the hospital,

00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:35.374
and they put them in a big jar.

00:03:36.249 --> 00:03:37.486
My mommy went there,

00:03:37.510 --> 00:03:40.081
and she took two from the jar,

00:03:40.786 --> 00:03:42.924
one for me and one for my sister.

00:03:43.725 --> 00:03:45.774
She put the seeds in her belly --

00:03:46.161 --> 00:03:47.353
somehow --

00:03:48.236 --> 00:03:50.543
and her belly grew really big,

00:03:50.567 --> 00:03:51.819
and there I was."

